Betty Fisher and Other Stories;;63;;92;;NC;;Grieving after the death of her young son Joseph, novelist Betty Fisher (Sandrine Kiberlain) enters a dark depression. Hoping to bring her out of it, her mother Margot (Nicole Garcia) arranges to kidnap another child, Jose (Alexis Chatrian), to replace the son Betty lost. Although she knows it's wrong, Betty accepts Jose as her new son. Meanwhile, Jose's mother Carole (Mathilde Seigner) is looking for her son with the help of her boyfriend, Francois (Luck Mervil), and some of his cohorts.;;Drama,Comedy,Mystery & thriller;;Claude Miller;;2002;;Sandrine Kiberlain,Nicole Garcia,Mathilde Seigner,Luck Mervil,Édouard Baer,Stéphane Freiss,Roschdy Zem,Alexis Chatrian,Arthur Setbon,Yves Jacques,Yves Verhoeven,Annie Mercier;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/alias_betty